{"tid":1568744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共煽動內斗係想將香港由國際鬥爭扯返落本地內部鬥爭","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:08:59.000Z","uid":62011,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"163641913ed413ce7829185db4097a43ac3a6297","tid":1568744,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"人權法係美國國會納入議程之後，中共港共有小小退讓，林病係呢個星期話推出空置稅，各大財閥商場允許市民入商場內部唱歌。 完全係為之後既內斗路鋪排。<br />\n<br />\n今日藍屍鬥唱國歌，撕連儂牆，打人，目的製造疑似兩派鬥爭既局面，依家CCTVB係咁播有兩派不同政見人士有衝突。就係畀外媒睇香港既運動依家陷入內部鬥爭場面。<br />\n<br />\n外國時間一長，外國就會誤會我哋根本唔係爭取民主，由我哋內部自己處理返。到時候人權法就凍過水。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋完全唔可以陷入內部鬥爭場面。<br />\n聽日915一定要繼續揮美國旗，唱美國歌。將香港放返入國際空間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於對付藍絲，人少則走，人多則打佢老母/私了。更重要係救自己人。"},{"pid":"c013a7e4c3ff2a0cd5f9189bec62bb9bb7b1893c","tid":1568744,"uid":299334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"521f146d4df993a8e578a2da23569ffaa6adda8c","tid":1568744,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ba4d457145000f0addeb51c5fa26da784c0d671","tid":1568744,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位幫手睇下討論下，將本地武鬥spin去國際層面"},{"pid":"90297abd785491645aeac40f6584d3cc97d635ac","tid":1568744,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:21:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"350c0661e547d16ca0529961dc17b3b52680e81a","tid":1568744,"uid":54921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>內咩戰鬥，唔好叫咩藍絲，叫民兵 藍衫隊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d99b46e3f2b97bb7f2a895b36f4af317263ee4fc","tid":1568744,"uid":243065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"學佢地自己燒"},{"pid":"730836cafe13faa76a6642b628f348270b033619","tid":1568744,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fcad25e467a2b28683efba751229e6e6c562983","tid":1568744,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n對藍絲，每人有3秒，開遮，做嘢，走<br />\n<br />\n對外文宣就唔同，用多啲時間，大大力繼續宣傳，琴日獅子山人鏈同願榮光要岀去，呢啲係文宣嘢就應該去文宣部，唔應該係行動部佔晒啲位<br />\n<br />\n開遮做嘢"},{"pid":"85252dd96e40951c94675c4fd472dd117608f742","tid":1568744,"uid":314947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"認同，幫推"},{"pid":"7f483dab87c6e4625f79a93a8702ed51be1ec6a4","tid":1568744,"uid":168359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"大家頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe06f54c724a8e97f9e21cf55da77ba44123ae","tid":1568744,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb43ca6f974301539500a8d923844c9f5ea03945","tid":1568744,"uid":19549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1f0d843243023f9db379ce05acc44ac51ac8b6b","tid":1568744,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"40a95c89da5b827ce4dde8a2d85a0a1f4110b146","tid":1568744,"uid":314947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"罵完班藍屍都要記得將佢地嘅暴行推出外國，俾外國見識下強国人嘅大劣質素"},{"pid":"c1b7a36adaff69f99a6140ead0fd8ff0568c3a08","tid":1568744,"uid":271235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"凍你老母"},{"pid":"49eaa791de0e81053b06db272e9349986ee68bc7","tid":1568744,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit